Fields for cdpartners:
1) selectableVariant: string
   - "default" or "xDemo"

2) sortOrder: number
   - the display order on a page

3) title: string
   - main heading for partners

4) subtitle: string
   - subtext or tagline

5) partnerLogos: array of objects
   - partnerName: string
   - link: string (url)
   - image: "image" field with asset reference

6) globalComponentSource
   - reference to another cdpartners object